short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension labels power supplies on PCPartPicker with their tier from a PSU tier list.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will try to match each PSU on PCPartPicker with a matching PSU from a tier list. It will then label each PSU with its corresponding tier. This will make searching for a good PSU on PCPartPicker easier for anyone trying to build a PC. The tier indicator can be seen beneath the name of each of the PSUs.
